title: PVRIS - Acoustic-EP (2014)
description:
PVRIS is an American rock band from Lowell, Massachusetts formed by members Lyndsey Gunnulfsen, Alex Babinski, Brian MacDonald, Brad Griffin and Kyle Anthony. The band formed originally under the name "Paris" but later changed it to "PVRIS" in the summer of 2013 citing legal reasons. However it is still pronounced "Paris", and the "V" acts as an upside down "A". They have released a self-titled EP and an acoustic EP. - Wikipedia
